OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774876271
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays Breaking Bad chat was 'not
OL,5,Cserious'
OL,7,FA man accused of causing his wife's
OL,8,Fsuicide by abusing and controlling her
OL,9,Fduring a two-year period has told a
OL,10,Fcourt that a conversation about
OL,11,Fdissolving a body in acid was inspired
OL,12,Fby the Breaking Bad television show,
OL,13,Fbut did not refer to his partner.
OL,15,FChristopher Trybus, of Swindon,
OL,16,FWiltshire, is accused of the
OL,17,Fmanslaughter of Tarryn Baird, who died
OL,18,Fof hanging in November 2017 at the age
OL,19,Fof 34.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
