PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774876271
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays Breaking Bad chat was 'not
OL,5,Cserious'
OL,7,FHe also faces charges at Winchester
OL,8,FCrown Court of controlling and
OL,9,Fcoercive behaviour and two charges of
OL,10,Frape.
OL,12,FThe coercive control charge alleges
OL,13,Fthat Trybus controlled Ms Baird
OL,14,Fthrough using and threatening violence
OL,15,Ftowards her, sexually assaulting her,
OL,16,Fmonitoring her whereabouts, limiting
OL,17,Faccess to finance, threatening to
OL,18,Freveal private information to her
OL,19,Ffamily and isolating her from her
OL,20,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
