FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774876271
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays Breaking Bad chat was 'not
OL,5,Cserious'
OL,7,FTom Little KC, prosecuting, asked the
OL,8,Fdefendant if he had talked about
OL,9,Fsnapping Ms Baird's neck, cutting up
OL,10,Fher body and dissolving it in acid.
OL,12,FTrybus, 44, said that the conversation
OL,13,Fhad been inspired by the Breaking Bad
OL,14,Ftelevision show - but was not about Ms
OL,15,FBaird and was not "serious".
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
