PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774876271
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays Breaking Bad chat was 'not
OL,5,Cserious'
OL,7,FHe told the court: "The context of
OL,8,Fthis conversation was a murder mystery
OL,9,Fshow, possibly Breaking Bad.
OL,11,F"Somebody might say 'How would you rob
OL,12,Fa bank' after watching a TV show, if
OL,13,Fyou were a getaway driver what car
OL,14,Fwould choose.
OL,16,F"It was just a conversation, no way
OL,17,Fwas it serious or threats, just
OL,18,Fsomething we chatted about. This
OL,19,Fconversation wasn't about her, it
OL,20,Fsounds awful now, it was about how we
OL,21,Fgot rid of a body."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
