PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774876271
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Csays Breaking Bad chat was 'not
OL,5,Cserious'
OL,7,FHe added: "We did watch Breaking Bad
OL,8,Fand I think there was a scene where
OL,9,Fthey dissolve a body.
OL,11,F"It happened on Breaking Bad, it's not
OL,12,Fsomething I would seriously consider
OL,13,For think about seriously.
OL,15,FTrybus, who is a software consultant
OL,16,Fand developer, denies the charges and
OL,17,Fthe trial continues.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
